Financial Services Cloud Bundle Data Mappings

The Financial Services Cloud data bundle for Data Cloud helps financial services firms increase employee productivity, accelerate time to value, and deepen customer trust with every interaction. These data mappings relate to Financial Services Cloud bundle available for the Salesforce CRM connector. You can add to or customize the data mappings.

SOURCE OBJECT	MAPPING REFERENCE
Account	Account Mappings
Alert	Alert Mappings
Card	Card Mappings
Contact	Contact Mappings
Financial Account	Financial Account Mappings
Financial Account Role	Financial Account Role Mappings
Financial Goal	Financial Goal Mappings
Financial Goal Party	Financial Goal Party Mappings
Financial Holding	Financial Holding Mappings
Personal Life Event	Personal Life Event Mappings
Topic	Topic Mappings
